{"tid":260360,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(而家先請人) FF7重製版招募製作成員","createTime":"2017-05-27T15:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T16:32:20.000Z","uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07eb3277169b462855a54b4ac926d84388ea1545","tid":260360,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係預左PS5先有得玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》是 SQUARE ENIX 在 2015 年 E3 展 PlayStation 媒體發表會投下的一顆震撼彈，預定在 PS4 上以新一代高解析度遊戲的標準，重現 20 年前《Final Fantasy VII》的經典內容，發表後讓全世界無數曾經歷過《Final Fantasy VII》原作洗禮的玩家為之瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n　　但《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》除了最初在 E3 展公布的發表影片，以及同年底在 PSX 活動中公布的遊玩片段宣傳影片之外，發表至今近 2 年都沒有進一步的內容消息釋出，亦無任何上市時程的具體資訊，讓外界相當好奇目前《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》的製作狀況與進度究竟是如何？<br />\n<br />\n　　如今負責《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》開發的 SQUARE ENIX 第 1 事業部終於有了動作，宣布將大舉招募包括企劃、設計與程式在內的核心製作成員。第 1 事業部主管兼遊戲製作人北瀨佳範、遊戲製作總監野村哲也，以及遊戲開發領導濱口直樹都各自在徵才頁面上發表感言，表示為了追求超越原作的品質，需要大幅強化遊戲的開發體制，因此大舉對外招募人才一同參與遊戲的製作。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前所開出的職缺分為企劃、設計與程式，包括戰鬥企劃、關卡企劃、背景設計、特效設計、動作設計、角色 3D CG 設計，以及程式開發。雇用模式皆為約聘，但有機會成為正式員工。<br />\n<br />\n　　雖然現在 SQUARE ENIX 宣布大舉徵才強化《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》的開發，至少能確認遊戲確實有在開發，但時隔 2 年才展開的徵才，不禁令人好奇《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》究竟要等到什麼時候才會問世？甚至能否在這個主機世代問世？先前 SQUARE ENIX 曾表示過《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》會拆分成多部曲推出，或許現階段該問的是「什麼時候能看到首部曲？」。至於「什麼時候能整個完結？」這個問題...只能就寄望後續的歷史會給大家一個解答了。"},{"pid":"d99c5a09ef72a797ed7502e3e15e8966ed0b2026","tid":260360,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"我睇到第二部ff15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ece76c5cadfa5308540376e83656d737415d97","tid":260360,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a669c200a36d4d98d88eb56c77690ac068e1c1","tid":260360,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8bc17685139a9e2d4ee7f65278870807ade5fb","tid":260360,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6fe2b405a5dc9ec2ca68356b62dab17889a2b1","tid":260360,"uid":93190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"可能PS6時才出到，因可能要十年才整好。"},{"pid":"4d10ddd66c7438cb0ad6b6ac9a80c888f9deb058","tid":260360,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"可能連埋psp隻前傳ccff7一齊重製"},{"pid":"c2b9e6aa7b4ff5e0fffbe09207cbc74feac0f387","tid":260360,"uid":7916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"SE:淨係每年E3換取掌聲就夠 唔洗真係出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cebbda5cf031f9fe2edecb1ab00ccb9d25b49b","tid":260360,"uid":119549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"由PS2 發表時開始造D CG片黎引我FF, 到而家都唔知開左個頭未, 真係陰鳩公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f4a6a3